{"tid":200721,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個對付仆街細妹既方法","createTime":"2017-04-14T07:58:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-15T17:50:29.000Z","uid":97948,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"70c38cba159240566da35733879bcf37d7f00d35","tid":200721,"uid":97948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T07:58:59.000Z","msg":"細妹細細個算係文靜 好少出聲仲好乖<br />\n自從入左U後性情大變 成日恰個細佬 <br />\n試過因為細佬唔幫手扔垃圾攞棍打佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家日日返屋企都西口西面 連爸媽同佢講野都十問九唔應 永遠得個西面樣or hea答 仲會鬧老豆老母<br />\n前排屋企有d事 老母問d仔女每人夾少少錢幫手<br />\n佢一句話冇錢 仲好串話要錢就冇架啦 少少少少咁比你囉 大佬 而家急事丫 分乜野期 搞到我媽既感覺好似乞佢錢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔講出面d人以為成家人蝦佢一個 唔理佢 實質就佢蝦曬我地全家<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多好多佢勁霸道既事 而家全家都冇氣鬧佢 就算鬧佢都冇反應 但佢得寸進尺 越黎越過分 <br />\n<br />\n有咩方法可以令佢識自我反省下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51fc6eb05cbcc2a9f787ebbbf62e30c6a48dcf30","tid":200721,"uid":103667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T08:00:33.000Z","msg":"以牙還牙"},{"pid":"35df1d4feac7b729b80b770881ea86227895bc52","tid":200721,"uid":24634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T08:01:04.000Z","msg":"趕佢出街"},{"pid":"44ece223ed1b4df89e0d00a7a223b0e74a15d805","tid":200721,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T08:02:24.000Z","msg":"比佢知邊個先係大佬"},{"pid":"cfc2dd6d517ab6038cfe5b6686487e85a13fce29","tid":200721,"uid":97948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T08:05:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>趕佢出街</blockquote><br />\n老豆老母好錫佢 話曬都自己女 都唔想鬧到佢離家出走<br />\n但我睇唔過眼 辛辛苦苦養佢咁多年 最後換黎既竟然係呢d對待 <br />\n好想有一日佢識反省 同老豆老母講對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1f9a8cdce07c2d6983505a75f1f26640d459eda","tid":200721,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T08:06:28.000Z","msg":"post佢屋企著短褲仔露腳趾嘅相上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ff0ec50f54db00cfbff0ab335de90d3e213fc79","tid":200721,"uid":97948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T08:07:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比佢知邊個先係大佬</blockquote><br />\n點樣令佢知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ee26e5d36109c2f109f9a1e8973de560838e121","tid":200721,"uid":15877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T08:12:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中</span></span>"},{"pid":"ef324d31a98fa2bcfd17d69ad3ac48f45ab58606","tid":200721,"uid":22888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T08:15:35.000Z","msg":"攞碌棍打番佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7704fc738eeacc508ccaf8aa6ace4c94f1ec4cbc","tid":200721,"uid":47857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T08:20:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">出</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1480d6f94aadab8f125ce97419b2140e30caf6","tid":200721,"uid":16685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T09:15:05.000Z","msg":"交佢比我，等我感化佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57aeb38e6cd684cd93ac5b6918622e239021ee38","tid":200721,"uid":97948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T10:18:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>攞碌棍打番佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n會唔會發生命案"},{"pid":"99d1fc176175de7141b09d90d9d5714e7bbec376","tid":200721,"uid":104833